AttributeList.Text: This function supervise Awake signal, - Awake signal is to test communication between PLC and IJCORE. - Awake signal is set to 1 by PLC and set to -1 by IJCORE alternatively. - first PLC check if awake signal is different of 1, if it is, PLC launch timer T1 (1s<T1<10s). at the end of this temporisation, PLC set awake signal to 1 and launch Timer 2. - if IJCORE don't set awake signal to -1 before the end of timer 2,PLC generate Time out fault for awake signal.
- if awake signal is -1 then launch timer 1
